{title: Big Rock Candy Mountain}
{artist: Burl Ives}
{composer: Written by Dave Fisher}

[C]Oh the buzzing of the bees at the cigarette trees
[F]Near the soda water [C]fountain
Where [G7]the lemonade springs and the [C]bluebird sings
In the [G7]Big Rock Candy [C]Mountain
On a summer day in the month of May
A [G7]burly bum came [C]hiking

