In the Big Rock Candy Mountain
The [G7]cops have wooden [C]legs
The bulldogs all have rubber teeth
And the [G7]hens lay soft-boiled [C]eggs
The [G7]farmers trees are [C]full of fruit
And the [G7]barns are full of [C]hay
I want to go where there ain't no snow
Where the sleet don't fall the winds don't blow
In the [G7]Big Rock Candy [C]Mountains
